      "section": [
        "Fire Nation train engineer"
      ],
      "text": "This engineer was a man who worked on a train in the Fire Nation and was involved in an incident caused by Combustion Man."
    },
    {
      "body": "One day, the ${link_0} on which this engineer was working was visited by ${link_1} ${link_2}, who was undercover at the time, and his friend, ${link_3}. The two also brought along a little girl named ${link_4}, who would be riding the train to get to her grandmother's house.",
