        "History"
      ],
      "text": "Sokka succeeded in opening the door to the cab after a bit of trouble, but had more difficulty in stopping the train. However, he managed to figure it out and stopped the train, while Aang managed to defeat Combustion Man. The engineer later awoke and discovered that Sokka had saved his train. As an act of gratitude, he gifted Sokka his hat. By the end of this journey, however, his train was rendered unusable."
    },
